; Test Lane — NGKs Crater Wardens V1
; Phase 3: Hazards prototype (Godot 4)
; ----------------------------------------------------------------
; Layout (ground surface at Y=550):
;
;   x=-400 ── x=560  GAP1(260px)  x=820 ─────── x=2900  GAP2(400px)  x=3300 ──── x=5820
;    GroundLeft         ↑short      GroundMid       ↑long              GroundRight2
;
;   Mine:  x=1300  (on GroundMid)
;   Rock:  x=2100  (on GroundMid)
;   PlatA: x=1600, y=500  ── SHORT JUMP label (Phase1 legacy)
;   PlatB: x=2600, y=450  ── LONG JUMP label  (Phase1 legacy)
;
;   HazardGap1: kill zone at (690,  620) below Gap1
;   HazardGap2: kill zone at (3100, 620) below Gap2
; ----------------------------------------------------------------
; Controls: Space=jump | Z=fire_forward | X=fire_up | R=restart | Esc=quit
; ----------------------------------------------------------------

